      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "European import GANDHI MAIL (3) makes his first Australian appearance for Anton Golino having put together a string of wins before leaving Italy. Has tuned up for his local debut by winning three trials at this circuit and distance and a good draw can see him make an immediate impact. GATESYS GEM (2) looks to be back to her best for this campaign having made a winning return at Melton last week. Races well second up so should be improved and owns strong statistics both here and at the mile. Can push forward from a low draw. Big chance again. YOUR MAJESTY (6) wasn't disgraced from the back row in the G1 Great Square in Brisbane last start. Had put together a string of wins and placings here prior so is better placed and could have a fitness edge on the top two. SUNNY GEE (1) is going well, coming from a 40m handicap to place on Tuesday to follow back-to-back placings here. Gets the inside draw so include along with COURAGE STRIDE (8) who draws out but hasn't been too far away of late.",
